Create a dummy all_lkps_maps

Source: R/dummy.R
build_all_lkps_maps_dummy.Rd

A thin convenience wrapper around build_all_lkps_maps(), using dummy data included with this package.

build_all_lkps_maps_dummy()

Value

A named list of tibbles.

See also

build_all_lkps_maps()

Other Dummy data: dummy_all_lkps_maps_path(), dummy_caliber_dir_path(), dummy_clinical_events_tidy(), dummy_icd10_phecode_map_path(), dummy_phecode_lkp_path(), dummy_ukb_codings_path(), read_all_lkps_maps_dummy(), read_icd10_phecode_map_dummy(), read_phecode_lkp_dummy(), read_ukb_codings_dummy()
